#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Reach the BOW Chamber"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"You've heard the plan. Ask the other survivors for our short, bloody travel "
"once you have accepted my request."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Good. Now go, we can't waste time in our current situation."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Well then... Lets talk about it again later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Those specimens are nasty in close range."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "We've got to get going."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Thank you. Now we've got more spaces to move around. That being said, tell "
"the others to stay put in this area... they also need your assistance."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Gather materials for SDP-L1 turret"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Gather materials for SDP-L1 turret'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Collect <color_light_green>4 chunks of steel</color>, <color_light_green>18 "
"scrap metals</color>, <color_light_green>9 electronic scraps</color>, "
"<color_light_green>9 power converters</color>, <color_light_green>5 copper "
"wires</color> and <color_light_green>a broken laser beam turret</color>."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"I'd like you to retrieve a broken SDP-L1 from the bunker and other essential"
" parts for me to fully repair the turret."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Then go, give them all to me afterwards."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "If it's too heavy, haul it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Good. The process may take an hour. While I'm repairing it, you should talk "
"to others if they need your assistance."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Clear the enigma chamber"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"So she wants you to clear out the enigma chamber, and you need my help to "
"access that room. But are you ready? You can refuse if it felt like a "
"deathwish."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Let's head to that chamber real quick!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Just ask me again once you're ready to take on."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Since this facility have come into chaos, we might see creatures other than "
"them."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Did you killed them?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Great! Lets head back to others and see if they need anything else. Enigma "
"chamber is pretty messed up anyway."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Really? I've come alongside you and yet you lied to something you obviously "
"didn't do?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Obtain a sample from the shapeshifter"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Obtain a sample from the
#. shapeshifter'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Collect a <color_light_green>desaturated resin</color> from a "
"<color_light_red>shapeshifter</color>. Use the tool provided to obtain the "
"required item then bring it back once you've complete the task."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"You must obtain a sample from that creature using a sampler kit I'm about to"
" provide once you're ready."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Okay, here's the kit. It is set to scan for an enigma specimen. I've sent "
"the coordinates to our guard and talk to him about this, he'll show you the "
"way. But remember, this creature uses deception to hide itself."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Be cautious on using the sampler kit, as it scans only the enigma, otherwise"
" you'll waste batteries."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "How's the sample?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"Well done, survivor. I'll start to identify this resin, and hope it can of "
"good use."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Slay the shapeshifter?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"She gave me the coordinates as soon as the drone reported her. I'll help you"
" out collecting the sample, and fend off this creature from you. So, are you"
" ready?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Good. The target is not far from here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "I never encountered this creature..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Wait. It's not the right one... I guess we lost it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid "Feed your flesh"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Feed your flesh'}'
#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\secro_missiondef.json
msgid ""
"\"Feed\" the bio-organic exoskeleton by activating <color_light_blue>Feed</color> command under the spellcasting tab (undefined by default). Alternatively, you can activate the <color_yellow>Metabolic Distribution</color> bionic, but it is advisable to use it only if you ran out of flesh.\n"
"\n"
"To complete this mission, obtain a <color_light_green>blob glob</color>. It's the main ingredient in creating food for your suit."
msgstr ""

