"We should go back."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "You need something, survivor?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We've got to go to the enigma chamber."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "What is it, survivor?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "You're skilled more than what I've expected from you. Good job!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Focus on our path! There's no time for chit-chats!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "I heard it. We will protect these people from the mutant hordes."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "You are not suppose to be in here, survivor."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Okay. Follow my lead."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "I know, now stand still and be a real guard."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "No, you're staying here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Do you need help?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "I need to go to enigma chamber."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We're here now."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "About the coordinates..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We're here..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Okay then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Nothing..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "We better go..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Nope. Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Not yet."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Nothing."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid ""
"I do need your help about a thing, but you should talk to our researcher "
"about this first."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I will."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid ""
"Good. Since I don't have any problems at all, you should check others of "
"their needs."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
msgid "Not until we get back to the others."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_guard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "Will do."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What is this place?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "What are you doing?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid ""
"Currently this building is military outpost. M1 might give you more specific"
" information."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "Okay…"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "I just clean here. Go talk with M1."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "Will do. Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
msgid "I'm security of this area. I serving under Sgt M1."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_miliguard.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Great job, survivor. I never expect an outsider help us with our dilemma, "
"yet here you are."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "You better get going."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "You are not authorized to this area."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "We need to go."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Yeah, and I want to know more about your plans."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "The guard told me you need assistance."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What's your plan?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "We've clear the enigma chamber."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Anything else I can do?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "How's the search for specimen?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Bye then..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "I am."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "I know. Just lead us all to that chamber."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
#: Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "Okay."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Yes, since you've proven yourself worthy for our plans, I'll be glad if you "
"help me with this rather odd request."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Since you've proven yourself worthy for our future plans, I'll be glad if "
"you help me with this rather odd request."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Tell me."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"But first, let me tell you a subtle understanding on our facility. There are"
" a total of 3 specimen variants: the failed, BOW and enigma, each in their "
"respective rooms."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Failed? BOW? Enigma? What are those?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Just describe what needs to be done."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Failed specimens are the results of unsuccessful mutations, otherwise they "
"are called BOWs. Enigmas, on the other hand, were formed using potent "
"mutagens."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "So what should I do?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Clear out the enigma chamber. That room were locked down due to extremely "
"anomalous threats, and you'll need authorization from someone to open it up."
" If you're ready, talk to the guard about this."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay. I will go now"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Excellent. Have you found anything of interest?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Nope."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"If you notice anything strange, just ask me and I'll tell everything I know "
"about that."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay. Bye."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Well, I'm curious about a mysterious, wandering specimen. Its the result of "
"our recent experiment using a highly unstable mutagen who, I believe, takes "
"form of a human."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "What do you from it?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"Unlike other enigmas, its genetic structure is of unknown form, and I need a"
" sample from it for deeper understanding of this otherworldly creature."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "So where can I find it?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid ""
"That's not necessary, as while you were dealing with the enigma chamber, "
"I've sent a scout drone to search for that specimen using a tracker device, "
"and it may take a while for its report."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay... I'll wait for it."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "The drone's still on the search..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "The drone has revealed the location of our target."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_researcher.json
msgid "Okay, what should I do?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "… oh… yes?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "What are you working on here?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "So, this is your lab?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "I'm working on the Flesh. Most of the time."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "The flesh? So you are kind of a doctor?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Oh not exactly, rather scientist. The Flesh is organic flesh-like matter "
"designed for wide variety of purposes. In short, it can be grown into "
"various tissues with various structure. It can create muscles, bones, "
"organs, glands, even whole self sufficient micro and macro organisms."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"My lab and my home. I created this lab long time ago when I decided to do "
"something useful. I believed that research on stem cells, cultured meat and "
"synthetic organs would solve many problems. "
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "That sounds interesting, what kind of problems you had on mind?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "You created this whole lab yourself?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Well nothing too specific in particular. Back then, goal of my research was "
"anything from efficient edible meat production, growing organs for "
"transplatology, various therapies with stem cells and most importantly "
"getting funds for my living and playing with life."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Oh yes, it took many years to gather funds, collect gear and set it all up "
"down here. Through years of my research I was leading various projects and "
"collected quite a lot of funds. Later on I had to tightly lock this place "
"and move permanently to other facility."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "Quite remarkable achievement, what forced you to move from here?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"I could either move with my research to more secured facility or loose "
"control over my research on the Flesh. I wasn't happy by that, boss hovering"
" over my shoulder, evaluating my work was hard to accept. Though considering"
" how it all turned out I'm glad they forced me back then."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "So the work under someone wasn't so bad?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid ""
"Oh it was, it's just that when everything went to hell, we had a little "
"accident there. Instead of me having little accident here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_s1.json
msgid "I see…"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What do you need, survivor?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "You need something?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Now that we're here, we won't be bothered by those shambling maneaters... "
"for now."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "No, this is not the BOW chamber..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Perhaps I've told you everything I know..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "You need to know more information?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"A survivor? What are you doing here despite the raging chaos?\n"
"Anyway, you'll be safe in here."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So what are your future plans?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm ready to push forward."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'd like to know more about the secronom project."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Is there anything I can do to help?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm ready for the job."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "About the repairs..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm a researcher."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Of what exactly?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Its not important, but if you wish to know, I don't mind ... since "
"everything's messed up already."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Then tell me your secrets."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Lets talk about that later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"... Its the secronom project, a project that involves human augmentation "
"using animal and alien genetics."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "And what's the purpose of the secronom project?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Human augmentation?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What about genetics?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I guess I've asked everything..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"For military, yet I'm not sure if there's beyond that case. I don't know "
"what it is, but the ones who can answer that are not in here anymore."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"You heard it. The government permits this project to perform human "
"experimentation. Don't worry, the subjects here are outlaws of the society."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "And what's the purpose of secronom?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "... but they didn't deserve this."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"We've extracted the genes of an animal, then mixed with a catalyst. The "
"catalyst is a classified object, so I can't tell you what it is."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"This is the secronom bunker, built solely as our last option for survival."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So why won't you escape this place?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Why is it connected to the lab?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Well? What have you earned for doing those?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"I know escaping is our best option, but what lies beyond the wastelands is "
"our main reason why we shouldn't travel."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So why is it connected to the lab?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "(pussies)"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"That's because we work in there, and performing scientific experiments and "
"discovering newfound technologies is our foundation."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Why won't you escape this place?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Regrets. I know you have encountered those ugly bastards, but they are the "
"result of our experiments. And the tech? All of them are incomplete."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "... So, is there anything else I need to know about the lab?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "That's unfortunate, but there's nothing I can do."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Well, if you're interested, I can tell you one thing... Deep below this "
"facility is a weapon of mass destruction, created for military \"use\"."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Thanks for the info, I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "My plan is a bit risky, and I'll need you to guide us all."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'm in for that!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Now, let's plow through the horde!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Good. We need you to help us take over the BOW's chamber. With that, we can "
"once again perform scientific experiments solely for our survival."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Lets go!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "... later, I need to gear up."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'll lead the way!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"This is science, you see? You may think we're the gruesome ones, but what we want is to open up new discoveries for us all. Yes, we messed up, but we're still here, struggling and helping each other to survive this nightmare.\n"
"I can't change your opinion towards us, but if you want to know more about the secronom project, talk to our researcher."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I see, you're curious about our \"unexpecting\" creations..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "What's on your mind?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Are those mutants in the city were the result of secronom project?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Are there some other threats this project has created that I need to be "
"aware of?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "...."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"What? That can't be good...\n"
"You know, secronom has an extreme potency of alteration once it comes in contact with a viable victim. If mixed with the catalyst, this will turn one's body into an adaptive living weapon, but that doesn't always end to the same result."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "So how did it spread?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"It is an unstable pathogen - evolving more by time, and due to the outbreak,"
" this facility falls into chaos; everyone panics, and got their body ripped "
"to shred. Secronom were doomed to spread throughout the world in that "
"incident."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Actually, there are 3 that we've discovered so far and maybe there's more to"
" appear."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Where are they? And what do you mean by \"discovered\"?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Those mutants think different than a zombified egghead, and probably they're in the woods, having a stroll.\n"
"We discovered them by applying a super concentrated type of mutagen into each of our subjects, and the results, few of them transformed into these abominations, while the rest died... which is unfortunate, as our team thought their masculine body can handle such potential power."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Well, now I know your team did an inhumane act..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"There is something I want to work on for our defenses, but they require time"
" and vast amounts of materials for the process."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Defenses? You mean turrets?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Take your time while you gather them."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid ""
"Yes, the autonomous turrets that you saw on the bunker is what I want to "
"acquire. Do you accept my request?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "Yes."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist.json
msgid "I'll do it later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I'm currently working on repairs..."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "What do you want to repair?"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "Let me check the progress of SDP-L1 turret's repair."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "SDP-L1 turret."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I'll check them later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I got nothing."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid ""
"It is done. I modified the turret and made it cheaper in power usage, with a"
" built-in storage battery."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I'll take it!"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I need more time to fully repair the turret."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid ""
"To repair the SDP-L1 turret, I need the following resources:\n"
"\n"
"4 chunks of steel\n"
"18 scrap metals\n"
"9 electronic scraps\n"
"9 power converters\n"
"5 copper wires\n"
"\n"
"It takes more than an hour to complete the process."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "[REPAIR]"
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "Perform the repair later."
msgstr ""

#: .\Modification Files\NPCs\Dialogues\secro_scientist_repairs.json
msgid "I need more resources."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Please leave anything in <angle brackets> unchanged.
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_flags.json
msgid ""
"This gear has been coated in bio-organic mesh, increasing its "
"<good>protection</good>."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_mutation.json
msgid "Experimental"
